Generate compound symmetric matrices

Source: R/data_gen.R
compound.Rd

Generate a p-dimensional compound symmetric matrix.

compound(p = 8, n = NULL)

Arguments

p

desired dimension
n

option to generate n observations from covariance matrix S

Examples

compound(p = 10, n = 100)
